info.name: Ticket Assignment - Flight
info.description:
### Flight Ticket Provider

You can use this provider to find and purchase different airline tickets. It has a backend based on REST APIs and you are given `"ViCyzlhQb+elxAbjKu9exg=="` as Authorization token. We have provided a Postman collection in [`Resources/TicketAssignment_Flight.postman_collection.json`](Resources/TicketAssignment_Flight.postman_collection.json)
This collection has three APIs:
* Getting a flight description through GET method by passing Id of that flight 
* Getting list of all defined flight in the systems and their description through GET method
* Reserving flight for a real person by his/her name, national id, and the flight id through POST method
